<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/564164-there-was-an-old-forgery-mentioned-where">There was an old forgery mentioned where two authors forged each other&#39;s signature in each other&#39;s book. Does anyone remember who those authors were? I didn&#39;t just imagine it right?</a>
