<div id="review_150663091" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/150663091" />
    <a title="Moira Russell" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1630617-moira-russell"><img alt="Moira Russell" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1256449807p2/1630617.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/150663091?book_show_action=true">Feb 26, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Moira Russell" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Moira Russell" href="/user/show/1630617-moira-russell">Moira Russell</a>
      </span>

          added it




        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1630617-moira-russell?shelf=2012-50-new-books-challenge">2012-50-new-books-challenge</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer150663091" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11819663486320231417">Well, this guy didn&apos;t love books &quot;too much,&quot; or indeed at all apparently; he didn&apos;t even like to <i>read.</i> He fastened on books purely as a cultural status symbol and that was it. Nevertheless, an interesting portrayal of a fascinating con man, even if told in near-enervating prose.</span>
  <span id="freeText11819663486320231417" style="display:none">Well, this guy didn't love books "too much," or indeed at all apparently; he didn't even like to <i>read.</i> He fastened on books purely as a cultural status symbol and that was it. Nevertheless, an interesting portrayal of a fascinating con man, even if told in near-enervating prose.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11819663486320231417" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

